metadata.name: Cyber Cafe [Magnetic]
metadata.description:
Commemorative musicNFT and Original 3D Art by Mr.Swe  
Our community is growing and our musicNFT movement is joining people, arts, curltures and traditions from all over the world and universe.  
My journey starts in November '21 with the idea to just try if i was able to do it in my life with my music, today became a everyday mission, and with this symbolic mint i want to just set a badge on the history of this journey with all the persons involved, collectors, fans, friends, family, and everyone close to me or my music. 

This is also my First on ETH Mainnet, And First Custom Smart Contract

Of course i hope you enjoy the music i produced and selected for this piece and appreciate if you at least take time to read this, and welcome to the Cyber Caf√©!
